title: Ice hockey players in Finland 2010/11 - 2017/18
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Number of players, containing a total of 8 data points.
Overall Number of players has increased over the Year.
Number of players is slightly decreasing from 2010/11 to 2011/12, gradually increasing from 2011/12 to 2013/14, and finally roughly constant from 2013/14 to 2017/18.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2011/12 and 2012/13.
The highest Number of players, of value 76387.0 was reached at Year 2016/17
Minimum Number of players about 56626.0 was reached at Year 2011/12
